## Medical Disclaimer

This software is designed for administrative and organizational purposes only.
It is not intended for:
- Medical diagnosis
- Treatment recommendations
- Clinical decision making
- Emergency medical situations

Healthcare professionals should always follow established medical protocols
and use their professional judgment when providing patient care.

The software creators disclaim any responsibility for medical decisions made
using this system. Always consult with qualified healthcare professionals
for medical advice and treatment.

---

## Privacy and Data Protection

This software is designed to handle sensitive medical information. Users are
responsible for:
- Implementing appropriate security measures
- Complying with relevant healthcare privacy laws (HIPAA, GDPR, etc.)
- Ensuring proper data encryption and access controls
- Regular security audits and updates

The software creators are not responsible for data breaches or privacy
violations resulting from improper implementation or usage.

